OL,3,CMoment 'gunman' pulled trigger in shop
OL,4,Craid
OL,6,FA man who pointed a fake firearm at a
OL,7,Fshopkeeper in and pulled the trigger
OL,8,Fbefore fleeing with a crate of lager
OL,9,Fhas been jailed.
OL,11,FLiam Finnie, 33, of Lord Street,
OL,12,FGrimsby, admitted robbery and
OL,13,Fpossession of an imitation firearm
OL,14,Ffollowing the raid at the shop on
OL,15,FCartergate, in March this year.
OL,17,FIn video captured on the shop's CCTV,
OL,18,Ffather-of-two Finnie can be seen
OL,19,Fwalking towards the counter and waving
OL,20,Fthe firearm at the shopkeeper,
OL,21,Fshouting "don't move".
