OL,3,CMoment 'gunman' pulled trigger in shop
OL,4,Craid
OL,6,FHe then squeezes the trigger, which
OL,7,Fclicks.
OL,9,FProsecutor Claire Holmes said the
OL,10,Fshopkeeper chased Finnie when he
OL,11,Frealised the gun was not a live
OL,12,Ffirearm.
OL,14,FFinnie was later arrested and the gun
OL,15,Frecovered.
OL,17,FPolice found it was a BB gun which had
OL,18,Fbeen painted black.
OL,20,FThe prosecutor said the defendant was
OL,21,Fheavily drunk and was taken hospital.
